00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:24,220
<i>[Zeng Yuhang]</i>

11
00:02:28,730 --> 00:02:31,070
- Mr. Zeng.
<i>- Hey, Ning Meng.</i>

12
00:02:31,070 --> 00:02:33,040
