21
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:53,450
No problem.

22
00:02:53,450 --> 00:02:54,720
Tomorrow afternoon at 2:00.

23
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,290
It's at our company's conference hall.

24
00:02:56,290 --> 00:02:57,370
Welcome.

25
00:02:57,370 --> 00:02:59,750
All right then. See you tomorrow.

26
00:03:01,010 --> 00:03:04,530
Ning Meng is personally organizing the promotional event tomorrow.

27
00:03:04,530 --> 00:03:06,450
Are you really not going?

28
00:03:06,450 --> 00:03:10,520
I don't have the time. What can I do?

29
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:19,220
<i>[Zeng Yuhang]</i>

30
00:03:38,220 --> 00:03:39,670
Are the materials ready?

31
00:03:39,670 --> 00:03:40,880
We're good. Rest assured.

32
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,260
Ms. Shi.

33
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:43,960
Mr. Liang, welcome.

34
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,100
Mr. Zhou, welcome.

35
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:46,270
- Please step inside.
- Okay.

36
00:03:46,270 --> 00:03:47,190
<i>[Eaglestone Capital]</i>
We'll head inside then.

37
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:48,820
Great to have you, sirs.

38
00:03:48,820 --> 00:03:50,360
- Ms. Shi Ying.
- Ms. Shi.

39
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,720
Welcome.

40
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:53,520
- You look gorgeous today.
- Thank you.

41
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,630
Mr. Lu is busy today.

42
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,360
He couldn't be in two places at the same time.

43
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:59,270
It's all right. Happy to have you two here.

44
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:09,460
Ms. Shi, I'm Su Weiran from BDI.

45
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:11,800
- You're Ning Meng's senior, right?
- Yes.

46
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,110
Thanks for coming.

47
00:04:13,110 --> 00:04:14,440
My junior is organizing her first promotional event.

48
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,880
Of course, I had to show support.

49
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,640
Thank you. Please head inside.

50
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,640
Mr. Su, this way, please.

51
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:57,160
<i>[Mobi Fitness Equipment]</i>

52
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:07,440
<i>[Smart technology awakens new fitness experience, promotional event]</i>

53
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:17,640
I'm honored to have everyone's attendance today.

54
00:05:18,350 --> 00:05:21,670
From what I can see, everyone is doing pretty well in keeping fit.

55
00:05:21,670 --> 00:05:24,510
I suppose you guys have been exercising.

56
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:28,570
Today, I've prepared a PowerPoint with 200 slides.

57
00:05:28,570 --> 00:05:30,550
The presentation will be at least six hours

58
00:05:30,550 --> 00:05:32,480
and it will cover all your needs.

59
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:38,410
Just kidding.

60
00:05:38,410 --> 00:05:39,620
Rest assured, ladies and gentlemen.

61
00:05:39,620 --> 00:05:42,830
I won't take up your precious dinner time.

62
00:05:43,820 --> 00:05:45,880
Today, I'd like to introduce to you

63
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:48,440
a cutting edge company specializing

64
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:51,010
in smart fitness equipment.

65
00:05:51,010 --> 00:05:52,920
Yunniao Tech.

66
00:05:54,250 --> 00:05:58,540
It's been five years since they invented their first product,

67
00:05:58,540 --> 00:06:00,660
the Mobi rowing machine.

68
00:06:00,660 --> 00:06:02,110
During the past five years,

69
00:06:02,110 --> 00:06:04,290
through constant upgrades and improvements,

70
00:06:04,290 --> 00:06:05,970
they not only had breakthroughs in their hardware,

71
00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:08,880
but they've also created software.

72
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,710
<i>[Mobi Product Line]</i>
It provides quality applications

73
00:06:10,710 --> 00:06:14,920
and allows users to customize their own training plans.

74
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:18,100
Now, we'll go over Mobi's aesthetics.

75
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:21,600
Let's take a closer look at this treadmill.

76
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:25,720
Its ability to fold 90 degrees upright means it takes up minimal space.

77
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,690
Also, check out the rear panel's design.

78
00:06:28,690 --> 00:06:30,620
If you place it in your house,

79
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:34,310
it works as a nice decoration piece.

80
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:39,020
The biggest advantage to Mobi fitness equipment is its competitive edge.

81
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:42,010
I'm talking about social attributes.

82
00:06:42,010 --> 00:06:45,110
This idea came from Mobi's creator,

83
00:06:45,110 --> 00:06:47,040
Mr. Lin Dayi.

84
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:03,820
Only projects with added value make money.

85
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:06,640
So when we invest, it's not only in the product,

86
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,450
but also its concept.

87
00:07:08,450 --> 00:07:13,010
Ning Meng. Your brief but concise presentation was very easy to digest.

88
00:07:13,010 --> 00:07:14,950
I have no objections.

89
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:24,280
Ning Meng, I'm in for sure.

90
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:27,880
How are you guys picking investors?

91
00:07:30,220 --> 00:07:33,500
Forgive me for my brazenness.

92
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:36,390
This project has very strong foundations.

93
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:40,150
So today is not only about the attendees perusing the project.

94
00:07:40,150 --> 00:07:43,820
It is also for the investee to pick their investors.

95
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:47,890
For instance, those with advertising and e-commerce resources

96
00:07:47,890 --> 00:07:51,750
will be given more priority for resource integration.

97
00:07:51,750 --> 00:07:53,570
I have e-commerce resources.

98
00:07:53,570 --> 00:07:55,340
We have advertising resources.

99
00:07:55,340 --> 00:07:57,530
I have influencers to promote the product.

100
00:07:57,530 --> 00:07:59,760
Mr. Zeng and I have plenty of KOL resources.

101
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:01,390
Wait, wait. Don't fight with me.

102
00:08:01,390 --> 00:08:02,640
If we're talking about resources,

103
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:05,040
I have the most comprehensive ones.

104
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,540
Mr. Liang.

105
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,590
<i>[Eaglestone Capital]
If you have a clear idea of your intention,</i>

106
00:08:25,590 --> 00:08:29,240
please send your investment share and amount to my email.

107
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:31,900
I will make a comparison and tell you the results later.

108
00:08:31,900 --> 00:08:33,470
- Okay.
- Thank you.

109
00:08:33,470 --> 00:08:36,340
Ning Meng, remember to keep my share.

110
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:38,040
The more the better.

111
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:39,710
No small share.

112
00:08:39,710 --> 00:08:43,300
Ning Meng, this young man seems close to you.

113
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:45,510
Will you approach him privately?

114
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:48,340
Mr. Liang, Mr. Zeng is my good friend.

115
00:08:48,340 --> 00:08:49,370
But rest assured.

116
00:08:49,370 --> 00:08:53,420
I will be open, fair, and impartial in choosing the investors.

117
00:08:53,420 --> 00:08:54,760
That's good.

118
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,660
You're showing no favoritism at all.

119
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:58,840
Is this considered a bad friend?

120
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:02,150
Sirs and madams.

121
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:05,690
If you have time tonight, what about we have dinner? I'll host.

122
00:09:05,690 --> 00:09:08,300
Never mind the dinner, Ms. Shi.

123
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:09,620
This is an amazing project.

124
00:09:09,620 --> 00:09:13,130
We have to hurry back and come up with a figure.

125
00:09:13,130 --> 00:09:14,900
There's plenty of time later to eat.

126
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:16,780
- Yes, yes.
- Am I right?
- Yes.

127
00:09:16,780 --> 00:09:18,960
I will be waiting for you all in Shanghai then.

128
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,570
Okay. See you.

129
00:09:20,570 --> 00:09:22,080
- See you, Mr. Liang.
- See you again.

130
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,400
Mr. Zhou.

131
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,100
- Goodbye.
- Thank you.

132
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:27,080
- Thanks for coming.
- Goodbye.

133
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,840
Thanks, Mr. Liang.

134
00:09:29,860 --> 00:09:31,230
This young man.

135
00:09:31,230 --> 00:09:33,850
- All the best.
- See you around.

136
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:39,030
The event was very successful. Congrats.

137
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,490
Thanks, Senior.

138
00:09:40,490 --> 00:09:42,710
Mr. Su, if you have time,

139
00:09:42,710 --> 00:09:45,250
why don't you come to my office for some tea?

140
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:46,760
Sure.

141
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:56,110
Ning Meng, you're free after this. Right?

142
00:09:56,110 --> 00:09:58,430
Let's go grab some nice food together.

143
00:09:58,430 --> 00:10:00,130
We're not trying to bribe you though.

144
00:10:00,130 --> 00:10:01,900
No, we are.

145
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:02,960
The event was a huge success.

146
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:05,250
You should celebrate a little.

147
00:10:05,250 --> 00:10:08,100
Mr. Zeng, allow me to put that on the tab first.

148
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:10,250
Now that the memory is still fresh in my mind,

149
00:10:10,250 --> 00:10:13,900
I want to get the minutes archived.

150
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:16,030
All right. That's fine. We can go another time.

151
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:17,980
Okay. Keep in touch.

152
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:20,860
- I'll send you our quote later tonight.
- Okay.

153
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:23,350
Bye-bye.

154
00:10:43,740 --> 00:10:45,320
Senior.

155
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:48,710
You're still here.

156
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,080
I just finished talking to Ms. Shi.

157
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:53,300
She only had good things to say about you.

158
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:56,040
How about I treat you to a celebratory meal?

159
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:58,280
I'm exhausted from working so hard the past few days.

160
00:10:58,280 --> 00:10:59,870
What about some other time?

161
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:01,640
I'll treat you.

162
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:04,480
Sounds good. Go back and rest well.

163
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,380
I can give you a ride.

164
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:12,650
No need to be polite with me. Come on.

165
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:16,100
Okay. Thanks.

166
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:21,200
Sorry, Senior, for inviting you at such short notice.

167
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:23,570
No need to apologize.

168
00:11:25,330 --> 00:11:28,350
Wasn't today's project the one you told me about at the cafe?

169
00:11:28,350 --> 00:11:30,540
Your friend's project?

170
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:34,110
So the "friend" was you yourself.

171
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:36,700
I've made a fool of myself.

172
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:39,390
We were in the same faculty. No need to shy away.

173
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:42,790
I didn't want your judgment to be clouded by sentiments.

174
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:45,800
I prefer to get an objective view from you.

175
00:11:46,700 --> 00:11:49,160
Honestly, I didn't have high hopes for this project initially.

176
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:53,030
But today, after learning about the upgrades, I changed my mind.

177
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:55,380
The project has a lot of potential.

178
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:58,880
This is totally unrelated to our personal relationship.

179
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:02,650
It comes solely from a professional investor's point of view.

180
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:08,000
To perform so well at your first promotional event deserves praise.

181
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,560
Thanks, Senior.

182
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:12,100
Compared to you, I'm still lacking.

183
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:16,520
Now Mobi has become a hot product.

184
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,540
Do you think I still have a chance?

185
00:12:18,540 --> 00:12:20,330
You wish to invest?

186
00:12:20,330 --> 00:12:21,630
Sure.

187
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:25,660
But you'll need to compete fairly with the rest.

188
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:27,760
Hope you understand.

189
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:29,590
Of course.

190
00:12:36,110 --> 00:12:38,550
Watching your presentation on stage today

191
00:12:38,550 --> 00:12:42,760
reminded me of the time I first got into investment.

192
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:46,430
I was also full of passion then.

193
00:12:46,430 --> 00:12:50,650
I did not simply give up on the projects I had faith in.

194
00:12:50,650 --> 00:12:55,620
But now, I rarely invest so much feeling in any one project.

195
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:06,940
Ning Meng.

196
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:11,000
Actually, I came today,

197
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:13,050
not because of the project

198
00:13:13,050 --> 00:13:15,050
or to meet Ms. Shi.

199
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:18,910
I just wanted to see you.

200
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:24,810
When I see you,

201
00:13:25,410 --> 00:13:28,200
I won't forget who I really am.

202
00:13:33,470 --> 00:13:36,650
The original intention I had when I first left the campus...

203
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:40,310
can only be found in you now.

204
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:04,280
<i>[Eaglestone Capital]</i>

205
00:14:04,280 --> 00:14:07,130
Ning Meng, congratulations.

206
00:14:07,130 --> 00:14:09,910
- Congratulate me for what?
- It's a secret.

207
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:11,190
- Ning Meng.
- Ms. Shi.

208
00:14:11,190 --> 00:14:13,250
Have you decided on Mobi's limited partners?

209
00:14:13,250 --> 00:14:14,360
Yes, I have.

210
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:17,310
In the end, I chose Mr. Liang, Mr. Zhou, and Mr. Zeng.

211
00:14:17,310 --> 00:14:19,470
The share ratio is 4:3:3.

212
00:14:19,470 --> 00:14:21,550
Okay. Get the contract drafted then.

213
00:14:21,550 --> 00:14:23,380
Manager Ning.

214
00:14:25,670 --> 00:14:27,850
Pardon?

215
00:14:27,850 --> 00:14:30,980
You didn't hear wrong. Manager Ning.

216
00:14:31,790 --> 00:14:35,730
Ning Meng, it's been some time since you joined us.

217
00:14:35,730 --> 00:14:39,600
For every task I gave you, you've completed it wonderfully.

218
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:42,090
Particularly the Mobi project this time.

219
00:14:42,090 --> 00:14:46,730
You were able to see it through even without funding from the company.

220
00:14:46,730 --> 00:14:50,030
You deserve the managerial position.

221
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:04,480
This time, the name cards are the real deal.

222
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,520
Congrats, Ning Meng.

223
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:06,590
- Congrats.
- Congrats.

224
00:15:06,590 --> 00:15:08,590
Congrats, Ning Meng.

225
00:15:10,670 --> 00:15:12,910
Thank you, Ms. Shi.

226
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:17,210
I only got to where I am today because you trusted in me.

227
00:15:17,210 --> 00:15:18,960
I mean it.

228
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:21,440
The road ahead is still long.

229
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:23,350
Keep at it.

230
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,550
We got you cakes. Come.

231
00:15:25,550 --> 00:15:26,320
Check it out.

232
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:28,370
Everyone, come and eat some cake.

233
00:15:28,370 --> 00:15:30,750
- Come over.
- Hurry over. Let's have some cake.

234
00:15:30,790 --> 00:15:33,260
And you guys, do your best too.

235
00:15:33,260 --> 00:15:34,240
- Yes, ma'am.
- Keep it up!

236
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:36,790
- We will.
- All the best!

237
00:15:36,790 --> 00:15:40,180
- Thanks.
- It's a happy occasion. Forget dieting.

238
00:15:41,900 --> 00:15:43,740
I have a teleconference. You guys enjoy it.

239
00:15:43,740 --> 00:15:45,540
Go ahead.

240
00:15:48,150 --> 00:15:50,670
Ms. Ning Meng, you've been promoted.

241
00:15:50,670 --> 00:15:52,600
Don't forget to treat us to a meal.

242
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,620
Will do.

243
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:56,950
Xiaoya, thank you.

244
00:15:56,950 --> 00:15:59,800
You helped me a lot when I joined the company.

245
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:02,200
