248
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:09,990
Let's have both. My treat. We can even have two meals.

249
00:16:10,060 --> 00:16:12,300
Great. It's set then.

250
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,990
Ning Meng?

251
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:20,410
Xiaoyang, you guys have cakes?

252
00:16:20,410 --> 00:16:22,350
