254
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:27,520
Did something good happen?

255
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:39,060
"Investment Manager"?

256
00:16:39,060 --> 00:16:42,180
Ning Meng, you got promoted!

257
00:16:42,180 --> 00:16:44,670
I'm going to take this back and show Mr. Liu.

258
00:16:46,670 --> 00:16:48,890
Investment manager.

259
00:16:52,030 --> 00:16:54,940
Mr. Liu. Look!

260
00:16:54,940 --> 00:16:57,950
